title: Start
body:
Clock strike 5.

		Jenny: It's 5 o'clock. I think it's time for me to go back.

		Jake: Hey Jenny! It's still early! You can stay here longer!

		Jenny: I guess Jake was right too, but I had promised my mom will reach home before 6 evening, what should I do?

		[[No, I pomised my mom I will be home before 6 o'clock.|GoBack]]

		[[I think is okay if I stay a bit late.|NotGoBack]]

title: GoBack
body:
Jenny: My mom felt glad when grandma told her I go back how now on the phone.

		Jenny: I think you should go back too before dark.

		Jake: Then, let me accompany you. My home is near with you, let's go back together.

title: NotGoBack
body: Scold by mom for not coming home on time because going home at night is dangerous.
